# AI Content Generator

## Project Overview

AI Content Generator is a dynamic web-based application designed to generate high-quality written content using Large Language Models (LLMs).

Built with Streamlit and powered by Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct) via the Hugging Face API, the application enables users to create professional emails, LinkedIn posts, advertisements, and conversational content with customizable tones, languages, and themes.

The platform integrates secure authentication, personalized content history management, theme customization, and a modern dashboard interface to provide a seamless user experience.

---

## Core Features

### 1. User Authentication
- Secure signup and login system  
- User-specific session handling  
- Isolated data storage for each user  
- Protected account management  

---

### 2. AI-Powered Content Generation
- Powered by Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct)  
- Integrated via Hugging Face API  
- Content generation based on:
  - Content type  
  - Writing tone  
  - Language selection  
  - User-provided idea or prompt  
- Supports professional, formal, creative, conversational, and friendly styles  

---

### 3. Interactive Dashboard
- Centralized workspace for managing generated content  
- Clean, card-based user interface  
- Feature overview and structured workflow  
- Intuitive navigation system  

---

### 4. History Management System
- Automatic saving of generated outputs  
- Timestamped content records  
- View previously generated drafts  
- Reload saved drafts into the generator  
- One-click copy functionality for reuse  

---

### 5. Copy to Clipboard
- Instant one-click copy feature  
- Easy reuse across platforms such as email, LinkedIn, and marketing tools  

---

### 6. Theme Customization
- Multiple pastel theme options:
  - Lavender Pastel  
  - Sky Blue  
  - Rose Blush  
  - Mint Green  
  - Soft Yellow  
  - Coffee Brown  
- Full Dark Mode support  
- Real-time theme switching  

---

### 7. Profile Management
- Upload and update profile picture  
- Sidebar avatar display  
- Account creation date visibility  
- Personalized user experience  

---

### 8. Settings & Security
- Secure password update functionality  
- Account management controls  

---

### 9. Help & User Guide
- Step-by-step usage instructions  
- Practical usage tips  
- Troubleshooting support  

---

## Technology Stack

Frontend & UI:
- Streamlit  
- Custom CSS (Pastel themes + Dark mode)

Backend Logic:
- Python  

AI Model:
- Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct)

API Provider:
- Hugging Face Router

Authentication & Storage:
- SQLite (User management)  
- CSV files (Content history storage)

---

## Summary

AI Content Generator is a full-stack AI-powered web application that combines secure user management, advanced language generation capabilities, and modern UI design to deliver a professional content creation platform.

It demonstrates practical implementation of LLM integration, user authentication systems, session management, theme customization, and structured content storage.
